6. KERNEL 4 — CANON CONVERGENCE KERNEL

(Full MNCC paper already delivered)

Purpose

Keep PantheonOS nodes in semantic alignment.

Components
	•	CanonDigest
	•	CanonDiff
	•	DriftStatus
	•	PatchBundles
	•	Sovereign consensus

Formal Rule

\text{sim}(C_i, C_j) \geq \phi
\quad\Rightarrow\quad
\text{Converge}

\text{sim}(C_i, C_j) < \phi
\quad\Rightarrow\quad
\text{Diverge \& quarantine}

